{{Infobox Government agency |agency_name = Defence Engineering and Science Group |type = Department |logo_width = |logo_caption = |seal = |seal_width = |seal_caption = |formed = |preceding2 = |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = [[Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom)|Ministry of Defence]] |headquarters = }}
The '''Defence Engineering and Science Group''' ('''DESG''') is a community of 9,000 engineers and scientists working within the [[Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom)|United Kingdom Ministry of Defence]] Civil Service to equip and support the UK Armed Forces with military hardware.
